LIBERTARIAN PARTY OF OHIO, et al., applicants,
v.
Jon HUSTED, Ohio Secretary of State, et al. No. 13A1089. Supreme Court of the United States May 5, 2014.

Case below, 751 F.3d 403, 2014 WL 1703856.
